<h1 id="get-data">Get data</h1>
<p>You can use the data.gov.uk directory to <a href="https://data.gov.uk/search">search and browse datasets</a> published by data owners from across the public sector.</p>
<p>Alternatively, you can use an API to search and get data from the directory.</p>
<p>Data from the <a href="https://data.gov.uk">curated collections</a> is not yet available via the API. <a href="https://data.gov.uk/roadmap">Check out the roadmap</a> to learn more about upcoming changes to data.gov.uk.</p>
